pageContext.claim: “Provide government healthcare for illegal aliens. Well, we don't do that, in many cases, for our own citizens. They want to take federal student aid, and free community colleges. They want to give that to illegal aliens, give illegal aliens federal student aid and free community college. We don't do that for a lot of our people.”
pageContext.analysis: Biden’s plan would allow undocumented immigrants to buy health insurance on the public exchanges set up by the Affordable Care Act — like everyone else. That is not the same as “free” health care.
